      en: `Subscribe to our free **newsletter**! вңүпёҸ\n\n**What you'll get:**\nвҖў Useful content about creativity and family time\nвҖў Coloring tips for you and your little ones\nвҖў News and promotions\n\n**Extra benefit:** Subscribers can buy extra giveaway tickets with their Peanuts рҹҘң\n\n**Our promise:** Useful emails only, no spam. Unsubscribe anytime.\n\nWant a **free mini coloring book** too? Download it when you subscribe! (10 exclusive pages) рҹҺЁ\n\nрҹ‘ү [Subscribe](/${lang}/#newsletter)`
