      en: `For **little ones (ages 3-8)**, I recommend:\n\nрҹҰҒ **Easy Animals** вҖ” Simple designs, 110 pages, perfect for beginners\nрҹҰ– **Alphabet Coloring Book** вҖ” Learn letters through coloring\nрҹҚ• **Pizza & Sweet Treats** вҖ” Fun food!\nрҹҳҠ **Coloring Emotions** вҖ” Learn about feelings\nрҹ§ё **The Cozy Kids' Club** вҖ” Cozy activities\n\nDoes your little one have specific interests? Tell me and I'll give a better recommendation! рҹ“ҡ`
