    recommend_boys: {
      es: `Para **niГұos** (4-8 aГұos) que aman la aventura:\n\nрҹҡҖ **Blast Off!** вҖ” Espacio y cohetes\nвңҲпёҸ **Awesome Airplanes** вҖ” Aviones increГӯbles вӯҗ 5.0\nрҹҸ—пёҸ **Mighty Machines** вҖ” VehГӯculos y construcciГіn (3-8 aГұos)\nрҹ’Ә **Awesome Boys** вҖ” Aventuras para niГұos\nрҹҰҒ **Easy Animals** вҖ” Animalitos fГЎciles вӯҗ 5.0\n\nTodos tienen 90 pГЎginas de diversiГіn (Mighty Machines tiene 100). ВЎDisponibles en Amazon! рҹ“ҡ`,
      en: `For **boys** (ages 4-8) who love adventure:\n\nрҹҡҖ **Blast Off!** вҖ” Space and rockets\nвңҲпёҸ **Awesome Airplanes** вҖ” Amazing planes вӯҗ 5.0\nрҹҸ—пёҸ **Mighty Machines** вҖ” Vehicles & construction (ages 3-8)\nрҹ’Ә **Awesome Boys** вҖ” Adventures for boys\nрҹҰҒ **Easy Animals** вҖ” Simple animals вӯҗ 5.0\n\nAll have 90 pages of fun (Mighty Machines has 100). Available on Amazon! рҹ“ҡ`
    },
    recommend_girls: {
      es: `Para **niГұas** (4-8 aГұos) que aman la creatividad:\n\nрҹҰ„ **Magical Creatures** вҖ” Unicornios, sirenas, dragones\nрҹ‘— **Dresses and Dolls** вҖ” Moda y muГұecas\nрҹ’– **Awesome Girls** вҖ” Aventuras para niГұas вӯҗ 5.0\nрҹҗЈ **Enchanted Easter** вҖ” TemГЎtica de Pascua вӯҗ 5.0\nрҹ‘  **Style Time Machine** вҖ” Moda a travГ©s del tiempo (4-18+)\n\nВЎTodos llenos de diseГұos lindos y creativos! рҹ“ҡ`,
      en: `For **girls** (ages 4-8) who love creativity:\n\nрҹҰ„ **Magical Creatures** вҖ” Unicorns, mermaids, dragons\nрҹ‘— **Dresses and Dolls** вҖ” Fashion & dolls\nрҹ’– **Awesome Girls** вҖ” Adventures for girls вӯҗ 5.0\nрҹҗЈ **Enchanted Easter** вҖ” Easter themed вӯҗ 5.0\nрҹ‘  **Style Time Machine** вҖ” Fashion through the ages (4-18+)\n\nAll filled with cute, creative designs! рҹ“ҡ`
